Package javax.constraints.impl.search.selectors

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractVarSelector
    This abstract defines an interface for the selection of the constrained variable from a given array of variables.
    ValueSelectorMax
    This selector selects the largest value from the domain of a constrained variable.
    ValueSelectorMin
    This selector selects the smallest value from the domain of a constrained variable.
    ValueSelectorMinMaxAlternate
    This selector selects one time the smallest and another time the largest value from the domain of a constrained variable.
